&lt;li&gt;Manage lead qualification and conversion from large financial firms, focusing on Private Banks, Family Offices, and Wealth Managers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively prospect and build new relationships with named accounts, establishing Addepar as a trusted solution.&lt;/li&gt;
